Lesson 13: Useful Verbs ===============================================================================================================================================================================================================
https://slovake.eu/learning/intro/verbs
To want	= chcieť.mp3
can, to be able	= môcť.mp3
to have, should (to have an obligation to)	= mať.mp3
must, to have to	= musieť.mp3

chcieť 	= to want
ja chcem	= I want singular
ty chceš	= you want informal singular
on chce	= he wants singular
ona chce	= she wants singular
ono chce	= it wants singular
my chceme	= we want plural
vy chcete	= you want formal plural
ony chcú	= they want plural

môcť 	= can, to be able
ja môžem	= I can singular
ty môžeš	= You can informal singular
on môže	= he can singular
ona môže	= she can singular
ono môže	= it can singular
my môžeme	= we can plural
vy môžete	= you can formal plural
ony môžu	= they can plural

mať	= to have, should, to have an obligation to
ja mám	= I have Singular
ty máš	= You have singular informal
on má	= he has singular
ona má	= she has singular
ono má	= it has singular
my máme	= we have plural
vy máte	= you have formal plural
ony majú	= they have

musieť	= must, to have to
ja musím	= I must singular
ty musíš	= You must informal singular
on musí	= He must singular
ona musí	= She must singular
ono musí	= it must singular
my musíme	= we must plural
vy musíte	= you must formal plural
ony musia	= they must plural

